Method Detail

postTokenize

java.lang.String[] postTokenize(java.lang.String token)
Process a token after tokenization.

Parameters:
token - The token to process after tokenization.
Returns:
Array of two strings. [0] = the token minimally processed. [1] = the token maximally processed.

The minimally processed token is typically results in an original spelling.

The maximally processed token typically results in a partially or completely standardized spelling.

These may be identical.

close

void close()
Close down the postTokenizer.
